(gen_random_uuid(), 'CCSS', 'HS', 'Mathematics', 'HSS.CP.B.6', 'Find the conditional probability of A given B as the fraction of B''s outcomes that also belong to A, and interpret the answer in terms of the model.', 'Statistics & Probability', 'Common Core State Standards', true, true, '2010'),
