(gen_random_uuid(), 'CCSS', 'HS', 'Mathematics', 'HSS.MD.A.1', 'Define a random variable for a quantity of interest by assigning a numerical value to each event in a sample space; graph the corresponding probability distribution using the same graphical displays as for data distributions.', 'Statistics & Probability', 'Common Core State Standards', true, true, '2010'),
